main event: A UFO was sighted for approximately 7 minutes over Tallahassee, Florida on June 23, 1966.
interesting points: The object was described as a celestial object with no optical sightings on recording tape.
The object was observed to have a specific shape, altitude, and color, but no sound or light intensity was noted.
The sighting was made by two witnesses, but no further details about the witnesses are provided.
The weather conditions at the time were hazy.
The report appears to have been submitted by a Major in the US Air Force.
